718447f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 63rd Street
718447f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 64th to 63rd Streets. The building with the flag, in left centre background, houses the Society for Ethical Culture School. At the extreme left is shown a portion
of the Century Theatre (1909-1930).
March 11, 1929.
P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
